      "message": "I did help with deleted entities, but you were right not completely. \nIt did delete an item from the recent keys cache, but not if they continued to show up in the query results. \nI consolidated KeySlice and keyContainer into the Recently type, that keeps track of added and deleted keys within the given time window. \nThrough the Combined method it will correctly remove delete keys from query results.",
