      "writtenOn": "2018-05-08T15:30:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It might be a good idea to mention here that Datastore docs recommend against using a key like this and YMMV.\nhttps://cloud.google.com/datastore/docs/best-practices\nhttps://ikaisays.com/2011/01/25/app-engine-datastore-tip-monotonically-increasing-values-are-bad/\n\n(The fact that this is a decreasing rather than increasing value seems irrelevant, given the explanations of this limitation at those links.)",
