        "id": 5120
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-05-08T15:30:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just to make sure I understand: We have to iterate through all expectations for any update, even if triagedDigests only contains name/digest combos that aren\u0027t in the TDESlice? Seems like that would be very slow.",
      "revId": "8d58f9fca4ac72850f01e6469717a153c502066a",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
